'''Musikagungs''' were [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]] proficient in playing a [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument. One of the most prestigious Gungan [[Band/Legends|bands]] was the [[Great Municipal Band/Legends|Great Municipal Band]], which was composed of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo's]] finest musikagungs. The band was conducted by musikagung [[Beezar Pert/Legends|Beezar Pert]] prior to [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]], and [[Augara Jowil/Legends|Augara Jowil]] during the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]]. Musikagungs performed the [[symponik]]s "[[Symponika Crunchen-Grand]]," composed by Pert, and "[[Symponik Nabooalla]]," composed by Jowil. The [[bawoonka]] and [[Drum/Legends|drums]] were some of the instruments used by the musikagungs.

